rows.label: campfev11_730_100_msg0001
rows.name:
Metsu is waiting for us in the Iiran
core, right?

rows.label: campfev11_730_100_msg0003
rows.name:
The way to the Divine Beast's core lies beyond
the Dannagh Desert and through the
Holy Gate of Altana.

rows.label: campfev11_730_100_msg0004
rows.name:
It's a highly important location to the
Kingdom of Iira, so there are usually
multiple safety measures...

rows.label: campfev11_730_100_msg0005
rows.name:
But Metsu must have used the seal
to blow past all of them...

rows.label: campfev11_730_100_msg0008
rows.name:
The Iiran Divine Beast has assumed
its true form.
